Philomina Kane bụ onye ọchụnta ego Ghana-America na onye guzobere Kin Apparel, akara ejiji nke nwere hoodies satin-lined na ebumnuche nke ichebe na igbochi mmebi na frizz maka ntutu okike. Ọ pụtara na Oge 13 nke Shark Tank wee nata ego $200,000 n'aka Emma Grede, onye nchoputa Good America na Lori Greiner. Ụlọ ọrụ ya bụ Kin Apparel bụ aha mkpirisi maka "Keeping It Natural".
A mụrụ Kane na New York na nne na nna Ghana. nwetara akwụkwọ mmụta na Mahadum Princeton ebe ọ gụsịrị akara mmụta na Ecological Biology.  Kane gbara rugby na Mahadum Princeton.
Tupu o guzobe Kin Apparel, Kane rụrụ ọrụ dị ka onye nduzi ahịa na mmalite ntutu isi, NaturAll Club.

N'afọ 2021, ọ resịrị Emma Grede na Lori Greiner pasent iri atọ nke ụlọ ọrụ ya maka $ 200,000. Onye America na-etinye ego na onye ọchụnta ego nwere ọtụtụ ijeri, Mark Cuban, nyere nkwekọrịta ahụ, na-atụ aro ka Kane soro onye na-etinye mbongo rụọ ọrụ nke nwere ike ime ka ihe okike ya zuo oke.
A na-arụpụta hoodies Kin Apparel na China.  Ha na-eri $13.75 ime na ịzụ ahịa ihe karịrị $80.

Kane nwere ọwa YouTube "NaturallyPhilo" nwere ihe fọrọ nke nta ka ọ bụrụ ndị debanyere aha 187,000.  Na ọwa ya, ọ na-edekọ njem ntutu isi ya wee nye ndụmọdụ iji “nyere ụmụ nwanyị ojii aka ịnabata ntutu isi ha.
